Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 6
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: The incredibly popular manga series that spawned an anime series, stage musicals and countless imitators gets a new printing.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 1
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Fame, romance and broken hearts. In this installment, Sho has one goal: to make Kyoko obsessed with him.
Title: SKIP BEAT!, VOL. 25
Author: Yoshiki Nakamura

Description: Alita is a powerful cyborg with a soft heart and a mysterious past. In this installment, the violent Zenith of Things Tournament gets to the finals.
Title: BATTLE ANGEL ALITA: LAST ORDER, VOL. 15
Author: Yukito Kishiro

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 13
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 4
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: From the publisher: "Darkness covers the earth, and the world is under the control of evil." Who will rise up to fight for good?
Title: 20TH CENTURY BOYS, VOL. 17
Author: Naoki Urasawa

Description: A predecessor to "Sailor Moon," this collection of stories has never before been printed in the United States.
Title: CODENAME: SAILOR V, Vol. 1
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: From the publisher: "Nanami is shocked to discover that the townsfolk consider her shrine abandoned." Will her work to revitalize the shrine pay off?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 5
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, learns he will be teaching English at an all-girls high school in Japan, but he must keep his powers a secret.
Title: NEGIMA!, VOL. 31
Author: Ken Akamatsu
